Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,, Miami: n.   迈阿密（美国最南的城市）\N They were taking a badly damaged boat from the Virgin Islands to Miami to have it repaired.\N他们从维尔京群岛到迈阿密乘坐严重损坏的船进行修复。
